plot: Supergirl and the team go head-to-head against Rama Khan and Leviathan; Lena and Lex must join forces when Project Non Nocere fails, leaving the two siblings in serious danger.

Lex gives a gift to Leviathan so that they can send Rama to acquire what they need to stop Supergirl. Meanwhile, Leviathan continues its plan to bring humanity under its control, and Lena struggles to get Non Nocere to work and faces a prison riot along with Lex and Steve.—Gislef
